ZH: 我喜歡在晚上看電視。
EN: I like to watch TV in the evening.

ZH: 他經常去電影院看電影。
EN: He often goes to the cinema to watch movies.

ZH: 她每天早上都會看報紙。
EN: She reads the newspaper every morning.

ZH: 我們去海邊看日出。
EN: We went to the beach to watch the sunrise.

ZH: 你想要看哪部電影？
EN: Which movie do you want to watch?

ZH: 孩子們喜歡看動畫片。
EN: The children like to watch cartoons.

ZH: 我們這裡有一個觀光點可以看整個城市的景色。
EN: Here we have a viewpoint where you can see the whole city.

ZH: 看著星星閃亮的天空總是讓我感到平靜。
EN: Looking at the starry sky always makes me feel peaceful.

ZH: 他在河邊坐下來看風景。
EN: He sat by the river to watch the scenery.

ZH: 她開始看小說時就停不下來。
EN: She can't stop reading novels once she starts.

ZH: 我們去動物園看大象。
EN: We went to the zoo to see the elephants.

ZH: 看這個美麗的景色讓我心情愉快。
EN: Looking at this beautiful view makes me happy.

ZH: 我們去看音樂會。
EN: We went to see a concert.

ZH: 我喜歡看電影以放鬆身心。
EN: I like to watch movies to relax.

ZH: 我們坐在公園裡看落日。
EN: We sat in the park to watch the sunset.

ZH: 他們約好一起去看遊行。
EN: They arranged to go watch the parade together.

ZH: 看到他們開心的笑容讓我感到幸福。
EN: Seeing their happy smiles makes me feel joyful.

ZH: 我想去看一場話劇表演。
EN: I want to go see a play.

ZH: 玩家們聚在一起看遊戲比賽。
EN: The gamers gathered to watch the game competition.

ZH: 她拿出相機去看看這美麗的風景。
EN: She took out her camera to see this beautiful view.
